*********************************************************************
************ PROPAGATION OF A PLANE-WAVE IN C-DISP MEDIA ************
*********************************************************************

Code to generate the plots in the section Propagation of a plane-wave 
     perturbation. 
** There are 2 folders: FV_solution and HOM_solution. 
** Within FV_solution there are several subfolders. Run psystem.py in
   each subfolder and then write_slice.py. NOTE: the data to generate 
   plots in the paper is included. This will generate some .txt files
   that have to be copied to the corresponding subfolder within 
   HOM_solution. 
** Within each subfolder of HOM_solution run solver.m. 

*********************************************************************
